freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Right arm rotator cuff pain issue still exists.   Left arm second shot is fine.
Same issue with right arm rotator cuff.  Not as constant yet still painful. This limits my ability to do much lifting.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: I asked that I get the vaccine in my left arm because the pain keeps coming back.  I have had a rotator cuff issue but it has been gone for a long time.  Just wanted to be sure it did not affect it so switched to my left arm instead.
I had my second shot in my left arm because the one in my right arm seems to have aggravated an older rotator cuff problem
Still having an issue with first vaccine in right arm and the rotator cuff soreness
Still in the right arm only
